Class GroupTable

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, RowMovable, View
public class GroupTable
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements RowMovable, View

This class displays the group information as a table by implementing the TableModel. The table columns are the parts of the pathname and the ordering can be shuffled.
